g t\u1ea1i 2 b\u1ea3ng A v\u00e0 B(c\u00f3 4 \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1) s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y 3 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh th\u00edch cao nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed7i b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi b\u1ea3ng C c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 l\u1ea5y 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n khi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 truy\u1ec1n ki\u1ebfp \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan, v\u00e0 \u00f4ng k\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2085","checkdouble":"193932"},{"date":"11:54 07/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Middlesbrough vs Sheffield Utd 01h45 ng\u00e0y 8/8 (H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/7/nhan-dinh-middlesbrough-vs-sheffield-utd-01h45-ngay-88-hang-nhat-anh-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay Middlesbrough vs Sheffield Utd l\u00fac 01h45 ng\u00e0y 8/8 (V\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Championship 2018/19): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e