\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, sau khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Sheffield Utd, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 r\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi 5 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Serie A, Inter Milan. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh m\u00f9a 2018/19, Sheffield Utd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Swansea ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Sheffield Utd y\u1ebfu th\u1ebf h\u01a1n do ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u0169ng \u0111ang ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i h\u1ecd khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf 3/4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Riverside c\u1ee7a Boro, Sheffield Utd ch\u01b0a th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o sau 5 l\u1ea7n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ecb s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Ben Gibson m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n sang Burnley. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Boro gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 quan, b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n Sheffield Utd. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- 10 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Sheffield Utd th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 3 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn 4 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2084","checkdouble":"193933"},{"date":"08:01 07/08","title":"Guardiola x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed sao Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/guardiola-xac-nhan-se-de-stones-da-tien-ve.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Guardiola x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Stones \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y trong m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tranh Community Shield v\u1edbi Chelsea h\u00f4m ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Stones s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola, John Stones c\u0169ng n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t gia nh\u1eadp Man City m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016. Trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi trong vai tr\u00f2 trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 thi tho\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tranh Community Shield v\u1edbi Chelsea m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Stones \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn khi Vincent Kompany v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ee3p Aymeric Laporte r\u1ed3i sau l\u00e0 Nicolas Otamendi th\u00e0nh c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Guardiola x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Stones \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Guardiola x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Stones \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/guardiola-xac-nhan-se-de-stones-da-tien-ve.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Stones \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c cu\u1ed1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Guardiola x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Stones \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi khi nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u201cStones \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong 10 t\u1edbi 15 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Stones c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u1ede Premier League c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i c\u00f9ng chung s\u1ee9c.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh trong \u0111\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nStones c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Kompany hay Otamendi \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd c\u00f9ng Laporte s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh 2 t\u1edbi 3 su\u1ea5t \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Man City. V\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, Guardiola n\u00f3i th\u00eam:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pep Guardiola\" title=\"HLV Pep Guardiola\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/HLV-Pep-Guardiola.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Guardiola x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Stones \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cStones bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao b\u1edfi Kompany v\u00e0 Otamendi c\u00f2n \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n. Sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t. Trong c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMan City s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn mu\u1ed9n nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng 1 (22h ng\u00e0y ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt 12/8).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man City tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-cau-thu-choi-an-tuong-va-te-nhat-tran-chelsea-vs-man-city-172-193815.html\">3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-02-man-city-ngay-el-kun-nhay-mua-duoi-anh-mat-troi-172-193813.html\">G\u00f3c Man City: Khi El Kun nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa d\u01b0\u1edbi \u00e1nh m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-khien-chelsea-that-tran-truoc-man-city-172-193811.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea th\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/diem-nhan-tran-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018-172-193809.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-02-man-city-pep-team-bao-tin-du-cho-nuoc-anh-172-193808.html\">Chelsea 0-2 Man City: \u201cPep team\u201d b\u00e1o tin d\u1eef cho n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2083","checkdouble":"193904"},{"date":"07:23 07/08","title":"Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110N\u00c1, HLV \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/tro-thanh-cuu-vuong-o-giai-u16-dna-hlv-dt-u16-viet-nam-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t n\u0103m sau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i U15 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, ch\u00ednh l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u00ea ch\u1ec1 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110N\u00c1 2018. V\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</h2><h2>HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110N\u00c1, HLV \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110N\u00c1, HLV \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/22/Tro-thanh-cuu-vuong-o-giai-U16-DNA,-HLV-DT-U16-Viet-Nam-noi-gi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U16 Myanmar</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 6/8, U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 2-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Myanmar. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i so thua k\u00e9m ch\u00ednh Myanmar v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cao nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. R\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc khi U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.&quot;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, HLV Myanmar \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi khen x\u00e3 giao cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: &quot;U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd tuy nhi\u00ean trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u00eam may m\u1eafn n\u1eefa. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.&quot;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0110N\u00c1, \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U16 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i Malaysia v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u16-viet-nam-vs-u16-myanmar-ngay-hom-nay-68-372-193846.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/u16-viet-nam-vs-u16-myanmar-ngay-hom-nay-68.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u16-viet-nam-vs-u16-myanmar-ngay-hom-nay-68-372-193846.html\">U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-2 U16 Myanmar (KT): U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1</span><br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U16 Myanmar v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o b\u00e1n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nVideo: U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-2 U16 Myanmar<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/6/U16-Viet-Nam-2-2-U16-Myanmar.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2082","checkdouble":"193905"},{"date":"07:40 07/08","title":"N\u00f3ng: Paul Pogba \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/nong-paul-pogba-dat-thoa-thuan-voi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</h2><h2>Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Zlatan Ibrahimovic, chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebf th\u1eeba. Jose Mourinho m\u00f9a n\u00e0y g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 Marcus Rashford th\u1eeba k\u1ebf s\u1ed1 \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 v\u1ed1n v\u00f4 ch\u1ee7 thay cho s\u1ed1 \u00e1o 19 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ly do Marcus Rashford mang ao so 10 cua Man Utd duoc Mourinho tiet lo.\" title=\"L\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/mourinho-giai-thich-ly-do-marcus-rashford-mang-ao-so-10-cua-man-utd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>L\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00c1o s\u1ed1 10 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u1edf Old Trafford \u0111eo tr\u00ean l\u01b0ng David Beckham (m\u00f9a 1996-97 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n sang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7), Teddy Sheringham, Ruud Van Nistelrooy hay g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Wayne Rooney. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Mourinho v\u1edbi c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y c\u0169ng v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i b\u1edfi Rashford m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 b\u00e0n c\u00f9ng 5 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o d\u00f9 c\u00f3 52 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd m\u00f9a n\u00e0y: &quot;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Rashford lu\u00f4n d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Wayne Rooney&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec Zlatan Ibrahimovic l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean Rashford ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng trong b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1i, ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i th\u00ec s\u1ed1 \u00e1o n\u00e0y \u0111ang tr\u1ed1ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, th\u1ebf n\u00ean t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o n\u00e0y cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marcus Rashford \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man Utd theo l\u1eddi hi\u1ec7u tri\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a HLV Mourinho. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Man Utd s\u1ebd m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Leicester v\u00e0o 2h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Marcus Rashford:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/rashford-va-chiec-ao-huyen-thoai-trach-nhiem-nang-ne-kha-nang-han-che-172-193843.html\">Rashford v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i: Tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-man-utd-chinh-thuc-tim-ra-tan-chu-nhan-cho-ao-so-10-172-193824.html\">N\u00f3ng! Man Utd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u00ecm ra t\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n cho \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-tru-cot-cat-giam-ky-nghi-tap-trung-som-cung-mu-172-192478.html\">3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9, t\u1eadp trung s\u1edbm c\u00f9ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bi-mourinho-thuc-giuc-dan-cau-thu-man-utd-cat-ngan-ky-nghi-world-cup-172-192455.html\">B\u1ecb Mourinho th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c, d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd t\u00ednh c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuu-sao-mu-noi-do-cho-hai-cai-ten-trong-danh-sach-den-cua-mourinho-172-192306.html\">C\u1ef1u sao MU n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong &ldquo;danh s\u00e1ch \u0111en&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Mourinho</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rashford-khoc-het-nuoc-mat-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-421-190997.html\">Rashford kh\u00f3c h\u1ebft n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2081","checkdouble":"193906"},{"date":"07:43 07/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 07/08: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chia tay MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/26/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-0708-them-mot-cau-thu-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-mu.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 07/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chia tay MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 0708 Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chia tay MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 0708 Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chia tay MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/26/tua.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tuanzebe c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Aston Villa theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, trung v\u1ec7 Axel Tuanzebe r\u1eddi M.U t\u1edbi Aston Villa theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y m\u1edf ra kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ed5 sung \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca g\u1eedi MU: 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng + Mina + Andre Gomes = Pogba?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ed9ng trung v\u1ec7 Mina v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Andre Gomes \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>David Luiz: &ldquo;Courtois v\u00e0 Hazard c\u1ee9 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i ra \u0111i&rdquo;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 David Luiz chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Courtois v\u00e0 Hazard \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, r\u1eb1ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kroos: &ldquo;Qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo&rdquo;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng, Real Madrid s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Laurent Koscielny?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wolvehampton muon mua Vida\" title=\"Wolvehampton mu\u1ed1n mua Vida\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/tan-binh-ngoai-hang-anh-muon-gianh-hang-hot-world-cup-voi-arsenal-va-liverpool.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Vida</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Domagoj Vida c\u1ee7a Besiktas thay th\u1ebf Laurent Koscielny, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chi 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Courtois</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Jan Oblak c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid thay Thibaut Courtois, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU ch\u1ed1t 120 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mua Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Paul Pogba chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Atletico \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Atletico Madrid mua Nikola Kalinic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, theo Gianluca Di Marzio \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid s\u1eafp c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb AC Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Real b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong khi Hazard,&nbsp;Giroud v\u00e0 Kante \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alderweireld</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Toby Alderweireld\" title=\"Toby Alderweireld\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/5-thuong-vu-co-the-xay-ra-truoc-khi-ttcn-tai-anh-dong-cua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Toby Alderweireld</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 khi Tottenham mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid nh\u1eafm sao Juventus thay th\u1ebf Modric</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic thay Luka Modric, Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2080","checkdouble":"193907"},{"date":"07:47 07/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Benfica vs Fenerbahce 02h00 ng\u00e0y 8/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhan-dinh-benfica-vs-fenerbahce-02h00-ngay-88-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Benfica vs Fenerbahce l\u00fac 02h00 ng\u00e0y 8/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Benfica vs Fenerbahce 02h00 ng\u00e0y 88 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Benfica vs Fenerbahce 02h00 ng\u00e0y 88 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Benfica-vs-Fenerbahce.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Benfica vs Fenerbahce</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Benfica vs Fenerbahce: 3-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Fenerbahce tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Fenerbahce \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 7 t\u00e2n binh, trong \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andre Ayew t\u1eeb CLB\u00a0Swansea. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phillip Cocu \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 (ch\u1ec9 thua 1/6 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 \u0111\u00eam nay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Benfica, Fenerbahce v\u1eabn b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n.\u00a0Th\u1ef1c ra, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua. L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Champions League l\u00e0 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2008-09. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Fenerbahce, Benfica li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Champions League \u1edf 7 m\u00f9a g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft (m\u00f9a 2011-12 v\u00e0 2015-16).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo m\u1ea5t ch\u1ee9c V\u0110QG B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tay Porto n\u00ean Benfica \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd trong phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n t\u1edbi 11 t\u00e2n binh. Trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Rui Vit\u00f3ria g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh Dortmund v\u00e0 Juventus (trong 90 ph\u00fat ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c) \u1edf ICC 2018. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Lyon, Benfica kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u1edf Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 n\u00ean Benfica ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00eam nay h\u00f2ng t\u1ea1o \u01b0u th\u1ebf c\u00e0ng l\u1edbn c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Rui Vit\u00f3ria c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1edfi 10 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng t\u1edbi 8. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n so t\u00e0i gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00eam nay h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1edfi Fenerbahce v\u00e0 Benfica \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn. 12/14 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Fenerbahce k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Benfica \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 2 b\u00e0n \u1edf 8/10 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- \u1ede Europa League m\u00f9a 2012-13, Fenerbahce \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Benfica 1-0 \u1edf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ Benfica (4-1-4-1): Varela - Almeida, Conti, R.Dias, Grimaldo - Fejsa - Salvio, Zivkovic, Felix, Cervi - Jonas.<br>\r\n+ Fenerbahce (4-4-2): Demirel - Ozbayrakli, Neustadter, Guveli, Kaldirim - Potuk, Topal, Tufan, Valbuena - Soldado, Elmas.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2079","checkdouble":"193908"}]}